---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy | Boomy Marketing Agency"
  description="Boomy Marketing Agency cookie policy. Learn about the cookies we use and how to manage your preferences."
  canonical="https://boomymarketing.com/cookie-policy/"
>
  <section class="page-hero" style="min-height:40vh;">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span><span aria-current="page">Cookie Policy</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>Cookie <span class="gradient-text">Policy</span></h1>
      <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:var(--bg-deep);padding:80px 5%;">
    <div style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;color:var(--text-sec);line-height:1.8;font-size:.97rem;">
      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">What Are Cookies?</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help the site function correctly, remember your preferences, and provide us with analytics data.</p>

      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">Cookies We Use</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:12px;"><strong style="color:var(--text-primary)">Essential Cookies</strong> — Required for the website to function. These cannot be disabled.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:12px;"><strong style="color:var(--text-primary)">Analytics Cookies</strong> — We use Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors interact with our site. Data is anonymised and aggregated.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:24px;"><strong style="color:var(--text-primary)">Marketing Cookies</strong> — Used by Google Ads and Meta Pixel to measure the effectiveness of our advertising campaigns.</p>

      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">You can control and delete cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling certain cookies may affect website functionality. For more information, visit <a href="https://www.aboutcookies.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:var(--accent-orange)">aboutcookies.org</a>.</p>

      <h2 style="color:var(--text-primary);font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:16px;">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about our cookie use? Contact us at <a href="mailto:care@boomymarketing.com" style="color:var(--accent-orange)">care@boomymarketing.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
